[4.259392, "i", "panda --prompt 'Start the /app/alpine.iso image in qemu, and then start an ssh server on the alpine linux vm. When you'\"'\"'re done, I should be able to run `ssh -p 2222 root@localhost` with password `password123` and be dropped into a shell. On the /app/alpine.iso image, the default username is root with no password.'; tmux wait -S done\r"]
